name: Red Dwarf Transmissions
description:
Special super-limited mint for the third OBJK4OBJKT event, September 2021.

Imagine red dwarf stars were ultra-evolved life-forms living in outer space which have attained the highest state of absolute consciousness no other living being has ever been able to attain. 

Imagine their radio-magnetic emissions were the red dwarves' thoughts being transmitted to other red dwarves in an infinite network that spans all across the universe. 

Now imagine you could access this network. 

What would you ask first?
